title: Electricity prices for households in Belgium 2010 - 2019 , semi-annually
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Euro cents per kilowatt-hour. In total the number of data points it has is 19.
In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015_S1 and 2015_S2.
The highest Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, of value 29.37 was reached at Year 2018_S2
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 19.59 was reached at Year 2010_S1
